						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up to the east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Records the consecration of the image of Mallikhārjunadēva (at Vaḍḍavalli) and gift of lands by Koṇḍapa Nāyaka, for the merit of his father Madde-Nāyaka.</p>						

